Class NameResolverRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.NameResolver.Factory
      • io.grpc.NameResolverRegistry

  • @ExperimentalApi
 @ThreadSafe
public final class NameResolverRegistry
extends NameResolver.Factory
    A registry that holds various NameResolver.Factorys and dispatches target URI to the first one that can handle it.

        public NameResolver newNameResolver(URI targetUri,
                                    Attributes params)
        Returns a NameResolver created by the first factory that can handle the given target URI, or null if no one can handle it.

        The factory that was registered later has higher priority.

        Specified by:
        newNameResolver in class NameResolver.Factory
        Parameters:
        targetUri - the target URI to be resolved, whose scheme must not be null
        params - optional parameters. Canonical keys are defined as PARAMS_* fields in NameResolver.Factory.
